rows.label: tlk000009_msg0003
rows.name:
Muimui-sama has informed me
of your arrival.

rows.label: tlk000009_msg0004
rows.name:
We have prepared a special rate
for your stay today.

rows.label: tlk000009_msg0006
rows.name:
Please relax and enjoy
our pride-and-joy open-air bath.

rows.label: tlk000009_msg0007
rows.name:
You still wish to look around the
Imperial Capital of Alba Margen?

rows.label: tlk000009_msg0008
rows.name:
Please come by when you wish to rest.
We will be waiting.
